Manusha katar [[Kyoto]] phenen ke ando [[Japan]] si dui sherutne forurya, [[Tokyo]] thai [[Kyoto]].

O them [[Israel]] prinjarel [[Yerusalimo]] sar lesko sherutno foro, pale andar o Israelikano-arabikano maripen, but thema thai e [[Phandle Naciye]] prinjaren [[Tel Aviv]].

Andi [[Jermaniya]] e bareder krisake instituciye ([[Bundesgerichtshof]] thai [[Bundesverfassungsgericht]]) si ando [[Karlsruhe]], kana o forovipnasko sherutno foro le themesko si kai [[Berlin]]. Varesave ministerurya si kai [[Bonn]], o purano sherutno foro le [[Ovestutni Jermaniya|Ovestutne Jermaniyako]].

